Variable Description: Name of the state that the constituency belongs to

For parliamentary constituencies: 3 digit code of constituency (e.g. P125 for Putrajaya is coded 125). For state constituencies: 3 digit parliament code followed by 3 digit state constituency code (e.g. N33 for Air Itam (P51) in Penang is coded 051-033)
Variable Type: string (3 numerical digits for parliament, 3-3 for state)

Variable Description: Number of eligible voters in the constituency
Percentage of Malay voters in the constituency
Percentage of Chinese voters in the constituency
Percentage of Indian voters in the constituency
Percentage of Other voters in the constituency
Percentage of Bumi Muslim voters in the constituency
Percentage of Bumi Non-Muslim voters in the constituency
Percentage of Sabah Bumi voters in the constituency
Number of early votes in the constituency
Number of postal votes in the constituency
Number of sploit votes in the constituency
Voter turnout in number of votes
